    </div>
</div>

<p><img src="/images/malta/kempinski/kempinski-19.jpg" alt="kempinski-19.jpg" /></p>

<p><img src="/images/malta/kempinski/kempinski-12.jpg" alt="kempinski-12.jpg" /></p>

<p>The huge balconies off the rooms are a delight. Just relaxing with herbal tea, some fresh fruit and watching the sunset was bliss after the noise and bustle of the city we had left behind.</p>

<div class="row no-gutters">
    <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12">
        <div class="post-left-image" style="background: url(../images/malta/kempinski/kempinski-32.jpg) no-repeat; background-size: cover; margin-right: 0.5rem; max-height: 600px !important"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12">
