    </div>
</div>

<p><img src="/images/malta/kempinski/kempinski-28.jpg" alt="kempinski-28.jpg" /></p>

<p>There are a number of restaurants and bars to choose from, all of which offer al fresco dining.</p>

<p><img src="/images/malta/kempinski/kempinski-14.jpg" alt="kempinski-14.jpg" /></p>

<div class="row no-gutters">
    <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12">
