        <div class="post-right-image" style="background: url(../images/malta/kempinski/kempinski-16.jpg) no-repeat; background-size: cover; margin-left: 0.5rem; max-height: 600px !important"></div>
    </div>
</div>

<p><img src="/images/malta/kempinski/kempinski-13.jpg" alt="kempinski-13.jpg" /></p>

<p>We only had breakfast but it was a gorgeous array of freshly baked, squeezed, juiced and sliced goodies. With smoked salmon, cold deli meats, salads and cheese as well as the best rolls ever, this is a perfect five star start to your day.</p>

